            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ")Neutrons were detected using modular deuterated",
                "scintillator array developed at the University of",
                "Michigan. The array is currently comprised of up to",
                "six 5.08 cm dia. x 5.08 cm cylindrical EJ-315",
                "deuterated benzene based scintillator and another",
                "six 10.16 cm dia. x 15.24 cm cylindrical",
                "EJ-315 liquid scintillation detectors. The liquid",
                "organic scintillators exhibit good digital pulse",
                "shape discrimination."
              ]
            }
